#: src/components/molecules/forms/Form.re.mjs:304
msgid "cancel"
msgstr "취소"

#: src/components/organisms/SessionEvenPlayMode.re.mjs:38
msgid "How many players should rest? (currently {0} players are resting)"
msgstr "몇 명이 쉬어야 하나요? (현재 {0}명 휴식 중)"

#: src/components/molecules/forms/Form.re.mjs:311
msgid "save"
msgstr "저장"

#: src/components/organisms/SessionEvenPlayMode.re.mjs:53
msgid ""
"Set this to the number of players currently resting to enable even leveling "
"of match counts. Set to 0 to disable and optimize match quality instead, but "
"this may result in some players playing more matches than others."
msgstr ""
"현재 쉬고 있는 플레이어 수로 설정하면 경기 횟수를 균등하게 조정합니다. 0으로 "
"설정하면 비활성화하고 경기 품질을 최적화하지만, 일부 플레이어가 더 많은 경기"
"를 할 수 있습니다."
